synopses.synopsis: Dick Tracy proved almost as durable on the air as he was in the comics. The serial came with the full gallery of Chester Gould strip characters: sidekick Pat Patton, Tracy's adopted son Junior; his girlfriend Tess Trueheart; Vitamin Flintheart and the villain, Flattop... - On the Air: The Encyclopedia of Old-Time Radio by John Dunning
